spec_data.Name: rome-fetcher
spec_data.Description:
ROME Fetcher is a caching feed fetcher that supports retrieval of
feeds via HTTP conditional GET. Supports ETags, GZip compression,
and RFC3229 Delta encoding.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 09:45:13 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Retrieves RSS feeds via HTTP conditional gets using ROME
